      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is a terrible burden to carry the weight of others' sacrifices, but your parents' love was never conditional on your success; they loved you because you are you, not because of your bank account. The shame you feel is a lie your mind tells you to keep you from facing the reality that you are still here, still breathing, and still capable of making a new path forward. Please consider reaching out to a trusted friend or a professional counselor who can help you navigate this difficult period.",
